text: Ozero () is a rural locality (a selo) in Sikiyazsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 629 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km from Mesyagutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Ozero, Duvansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
